{
  "text": "Reminding that in this case, an exact decoupling of flapping-lagging-transverse shear motion from the extensiontwist is obtained, the dynamic equations of pretwist rotating blades of nonuniform cross-section in terms of bending displacement variables are as (Song et al. [CITATION_1] , Na and Librescu [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] )",
  "citation_candidates": [
